This movie gets better with each watch. I think I have seen it 6 or 7 times already so decided it was time to own it.
A love story that was well directed and acted. Loved the story and the theme song. A welcome addition to my love movie collection.
Got it as a gift for some workers in a local Saloon. They really appreciated the thought. Also, I would recommend this movie to anyone who enjoys a cute story. The music also is a plus.

I didn't think the quality of the DVD itself was very good.  It seemed to pixelate and break up on my HD TV.  It wasn't up to par with the other DVDs I have from Star Cinema.  The storyline was fairly good but you have to be ok with an unhappy ending.
It's not as good as I expected.  Lowsy story.
